##
## Minimize build context for docker/openresty/Dockerfile.
##
## The runtime image only needs:
## - OpenResty (nginx + Lua) sources under `openresty/`
## - Runtime daemons under `srv/fn/runtimes/`
## - Default functions root placeholder under `srv/fn/functions/`
## - Docker entrypoints under `docker/openresty/`
##
## Everything else (docs, examples, tests, sdk, local artifacts) is mounted at
## runtime or used outside the image build and should not slow `docker compose build`.
##

# Ignore everything by default.
**

# Allow the minimal build inputs.
!.dockerignore
!docker/
!docker/openresty/
!docker/openresty/Dockerfile
!docker/openresty/start.sh
!openresty/
!openresty/**
!srv/
!srv/fn/
!srv/fn/runtimes/
!srv/fn/runtimes/**
!srv/fn/functions/
!srv/fn/functions/**

